{"tid":48452,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2個星期玩唔玩到倫敦同德國","createTime":"2016-12-21T05:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T12:08:46.000Z","uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a6466a7960328d784cb6845732562d06467eb3","tid":48452,"uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"4月打算自己一個去歐洲玩2星期(已扣飛機頭尾2日)<br />\n第1次衝出亞洲 亦上過背包客棧爬文<br />\n打算飛倫敦 之後去柏林同其他德國地方&gt;奧地利&gt;最後蒙尼黑返香港<br />\n初步計劃倫敦玩5日 德國玩1星期 中間可能奧地利玩2日<br />\ndetail既唔洗plan住 想問下咁樣大致上有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果玩多1星期寧願去埋巴黎定玩耐d奧地利+捷克?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db9560ada1b650366f008ced92d31a7d63a8f31","tid":48452,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"睇你點樣玩嘅啫<br />\n我玩過廿日德國 覺得有啲地方多咗<br />\n有啲就未去夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴黎唔係咁多嘢玩 四日都好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係我會揀奧地利+捷克"},{"pid":"f1d76368e4df2ed6f5a06d4850371cedc08c3af2","tid":48452,"uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你點樣玩嘅啫<br />\n我玩過廿日德國 覺得有啲地方多咗<br />\n有啲就未去夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴黎唔係咁多嘢玩 四日都好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係我會揀奧地利+捷克</blockquote><br />\n我見巴黎都係多藝術館果d 自己唔太大興趣"},{"pid":"81a9e6f4daf40599ca722ca6ddb9624f57ef53c1","tid":48452,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你點樣玩嘅啫<br />\n我玩過廿日德國 覺得有啲地方多咗<br />\n有啲就未去夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴黎唔係咁多嘢玩 四日都好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係我會揀奧地利+捷克</blockquote><br />\n我見巴黎都係多藝術館果d 自己唔太大興趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴黎市